<span id="freeTextContainer4497381512931014984"><strong>A good read for this genre</strong><br/><br/>Not bad at all, one should read this book&apos;s precursor first. The two combined are a good read.<br/><br/>Not a five but a decent 4 .<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText4497381512931014984" style="display:none"><strong>A good read for this genre</strong><br /><br />Not bad at all, one should read this book's precursor first. The two combined are a good read.<br /><br />Not a five but a decent 4 .<br /></span>
