<span id="freeTextContainer16715626703293713356">I absolutely LOVED The Gomorrah Principle!! As I was reading it, there were a few times when I said to myself, &quot;A friend of MINE wrote this awesome book!&quot; It was filled with suspense, thrills, chills and I know I choked down a few tears when Lacey sang at The Opry. I love the fact the Lacey&apos;s story was weaved into the fabric of the novel. I cheered for her numerous times! The Gomorrah Principle was SO much more than a Vietnam Sniper&apos;s Story.... it was a story of love, vengeance, temptation and a</span>
