<span id="freeTextContainer9370399222826142890">The Gomorrah Principle: A Vietnam Sniper&apos;s Story by Rick DeStefanis is a remarkable work of fiction that resonates with truth. The story captures the ambiguities of the Vietnam War, to a degree really any war. It also places at front and center the value of human relationships, especially those between loved ones. It is well-written with fast-paced action and timing that is hard to beat, easily a one-sitting read over a weekend. It can be appreciated by men and women of any generation, warrior o</span>
  <span id="freeText9370399222826142890" style="display:none">The Gomorrah Principle: A Vietnam Sniper's Story by Rick DeStefanis is a remarkable work of fiction that resonates with truth. The story captures the ambiguities of the Vietnam War, to a degree really any war. It also places at front and center the value of human relationships, especially those between loved ones. It is well-written with fast-paced action and timing that is hard to beat, easily a one-sitting read over a weekend. It can be appreciated by men and women of any generation, warrior or not. Thank you to the author and to Goodreads for sharing this title!</span>
