<span id="freeTextContainer4844694535897516875">WOW! What a GREAT read. I picked this up at a Memphis, Tennessee Barnes and Noble when I was visiting on business. Written by an army vet, this is an excellent story of combat, with a love story and a murder mystery woven in for good measure. Political intrigue, double agents, battle-proven military snipers, that goes from the jungle of Vietnam to the hills of Tennessee. This is apparently this author&apos;s first novel, but I certainly hope that it is not his last. WARNING, not a spoiler alert. Once</span>
