<div id="review_779943007" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/779943007" />
    <a title="Karin" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3369592-karin"><img alt="Karin" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1347580936p2/3369592.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/779943007?book_show_action=true">Dec 03, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Karin" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Karin" href="/user/show/3369592-karin">Karin</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3369592-karin?shelf=first-reads">first-reads</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer779943007" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18053662197218449724">The title suggests a war story, but it is much more than that. It is a story of revenge for a fallen friend and a love story. I had never read a story involving the Vietnam war. For me personally, it helped to know more about the day to day experiences my Dad may have had. I enjoyed the characters and the way the author set the scenes. I could picture the landscape without it being overtly descriptive. I recommend this book to anyone who likes love stories, mysteries or just a good story. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


