              <span id="reviewTextContainer1271887795" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1726130903644631292">I want to thank my daughter for sharing <i>The Gomorrah Principle</i> that she won on Goodreads First Read Giveaway and Rich DeStefanis, the author.<br/><br/><i>The Gomorrah Principle</i> is a tale of intrigue, corruption and romance following the hero Brady Nash, as he gathers evidence that his step-brother was murdered in VietNam by a CIA operative. It is an excellent and exciting story that I loved.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

